name: DynAsana
description:
DynAsana is a Dynamo package providing integration with task management app Asana, allowing you to retrieve & create tasks. Currently includes support for retrieving most Asana objects (such as Tasks, Projects, Users, Tags) and creating Tasks, Projects & Tags. Future updates will enable modification & deletion of existing items & support for OAuth flow.

	This is an open-source package, please visit repository ( https://github.com/radumg/DynAsana ) to submit improvement requests, bug reports or to contribute. Alternatively, tweet at me @radugidei .
